PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781104294
OL,3,CCumbria's Ben Stokes dropped from
OL,4,CEngland Squad over nightclub incident
OL,6,FThey remain subject to an internal
OL,7,Finvestigation by the England and Wales
OL,8,FCricket Board ` and another by the
OL,9,Findependent Cricket Regulator ` but
OL,10,Ffears that Stokes was ready to stand
OL,11,Fdown as skipper, or even announce his
OL,12,Finternational retirement have cooled.
OL,14,FInstead, the ECB has bought some time
OL,15,Fby leaving both men out of next
OL,16,FWednesday's clash at the Kia Oval
OL,17,Fwithout administering any formal
OL,18,Fdisciplinary action.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
