PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781104294
OL,3,CCumbria's Ben Stokes dropped from
OL,4,CEngland Squad over nightclub incident
OL,6,FHarry Brook has not stepped up from
OL,7,Fhis role as vice-captain. That role
OL,8,Fgoes to Root, who held the post for
OL,9,Ffive years before stepping down in
OL,10,F2022 and is viewed as the most mature
OL,11,Fpresence in a dressing room that has
OL,12,Ffaced plentiful criticism of its
OL,13,Fprofessionalism.
OL,15,FBrook was involved in a nightclub
OL,16,Faltercation of his own on the pre-
OL,17,FAshes tour of New Zealand in November,
OL,18,Fstruck by a bouncer after a late night
OL,19,Fdrinking session the night before an
OL,20,FODI in Wellington.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
