FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781104294
OL,3,CCumbria's Ben Stokes dropped from
OL,4,CEngland Squad over nightclub incident
OL,6,FThere was no curfew in place at the
OL,7,Ftime but he was heavily fined, given a
OL,8,Ffinal warning and censured by the
OL,9,FCricket Regulator.
OL,11,FRoot, meanwhile, has a near flawless
OL,12,Fdisciplinary record and can be relied
OL,13,Fupon as the ultimate 'safe pair of
OL,14,Fhands' in what is likely to be an
OL,15,Fextremely challenging week off the
OL,16,Ffield.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
